<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>
  XQ Tech Solutions ("we," "our," or "us") operates the Paal Pannai mobile and web
  application (the "App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose,
  and safeguard your information when you use our App.
</p>
<p>
  By using Paal Pannai, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance
  with this Privacy Policy.
</p>

<hr />

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<h3>1. Personal Information</h3>
<p>When you register and use our App, we may collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email address and password for authentication</li>
  <li><strong>Profile Information:</strong> Name and contact details you choose to provide</li>
</ul>

<h3>2. Farm and Livestock Data</h3>
<p>To provide our livestock management services, we collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Animal Records:</strong> Animal names, identification numbers, dates of birth, breed/category (cow/buffalo), gender, images, and lifecycle stage</li>
  <li><strong>Health Records:</strong> Vaccination schedules, deworming records, veterinary visits, and health task reminders</li>
  <li><strong>Breeding Records:</strong> Artificial insemination (AI) dates, heat cycles, pregnancy checks, and calving information</li>
  <li><strong>Milk Production Data:</strong> Daily milk yield entries, production reports, and trends</li>
  <li><strong>Feed and Nutrition Data:</strong> Feed entries, nutritional calculations, and feed inventory</li>
  <li><strong>Financial Records:</strong> Milk sales, expenses, and profit/loss summaries</li>
</ul>

<h3>3. Device and Usage Information</h3>
<p>We automatically collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, and app version</li>
  <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Features accessed, timestamps, and interaction patterns</li>
  <li><strong>Notification Preferences:</strong> Settings for task reminders and alerts</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use the collected information to:</p>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Provide Services:</strong> Manage your livestock records, generate health reminders, calculate feed nutrition, and track milk production</li>
  <li><strong>Send Notifications:</strong> Deliver task reminders, vaccination alerts, and breeding cycle notifications</li>
  <li><strong>Generate Reports:</strong> Create milk production reports, expense summaries, and profit/loss statements</li>
  <li><strong>Improve the App:</strong> Analyze usage patterns to enhance features and user experience</li>
  <li><strong>Provide Support:</strong> Respond to your inquiries and technical issues</li>
  <li><strong>Ensure Security:</strong> Protect against unauthorized access and maintain data integrity</li>
</ol>

<hr />

<h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>

<h3>Storage</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Cloud Storage:</strong> Your data is stored securely on Firebase (Google Cloud Platform) servers</li>
  <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> Some data is cached locally on your device using Hive for offline access</li>
  <li><strong>Data Sync:</strong> Information synchronizes between your device and cloud when connected to the internet</li>
</ul>

<h3>Security Measures</h3>
<p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Secure authentication via Firebase Authentication</li>
  <li>Encrypted data transmission (HTTPS/TLS)</li>
  <li>Access controls limiting data access to authenticated users only</li>
  <li>Regular security assessments and updates</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
<p>We do <strong>NOT</strong> sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.</p>
<p>We may share your information only in the following circumstances:</p>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> With trusted third-party services (Firebase/Google) that help us operate the App, subject to confidentiality agreements</li>
  <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law, court order, or government regulation</li>
  <li><strong>Protection of Rights:</strong> To protect the rights, property, or safety of XQ Tech Solutions, our users, or others</li>
  <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with any merger, acquisition, or sale of company assets (with prior notice)</li>
</ol>

<hr />

<h2>Your Rights and Choices</h2>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Access:</strong> View all your data stored in the App</li>
  <li><strong>Update:</strong> Modify your personal and farm information at any time</li>
  <li><strong>Delete:</strong> Request deletion of your account and associated data</li>
  <li><strong>Export:</strong> Download your data in standard formats (Excel/PDF reports)</li>
  <li><strong>Notifications:</strong> Control push notification preferences in app settings</li>
  <li><strong>Withdraw Consent:</strong> Stop using the App at any time</li>
</ol>
<p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@xqtechsolutions.com">admin@xqtechsolutions.com</a>.</p>

<hr />

<h2>Data Retention</h2>
<ul>
  <li>We retain your data as long as your account is active</li>
  <li>Upon account deletion request, we will delete your personal data within 30 days</li>
  <li>Some anonymized data may be retained for analytical purposes</li>
  <li>Backup data may persist for up to 90 days before complete removal</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>
  Paal Pannai is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly
  collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected
  information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately.
</p>

